{"tid":1023982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎有意簽下麥巴比","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T04:11:44.000Z","uid":14454,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"64fed170296edde963c418455f0ae583dc95d4a7","tid":1023982,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"來自西班牙《阿斯報》的消息，法甲豪門巴黎聖日耳門正計劃於短期內，引進一名備受國內媒體關注的超級新星，他的名字是麥巴比。的而且確，這名獲得PSG覬覦的球員，確實是叫麥巴比，但他並非現時於杜曹麾下披上7號球衣的那一位，而是一位年僅11歲的小小將。<br />\n<br />\n作為法國U-12成員之一的「小麥巴比」，全名 Kylian Mbappe Ndoumbe Yaba，與現時於巴黎聖日耳門一隊佔有主力席位的麥巴比（Kylian Sanmi Mbappe Lottin），有著非常類近的名字。據了解，只得11歲的他，同樣是司職翼鋒，亦擅長以速度壓制對手，所以這名超級新人的外號，正是「新麥巴比」。《阿斯報》指出，巴黎聖日耳門正與「小麥巴比」的所屬球會 Roissy-en-Brie 和其家人接觸，並表達了有意簽人的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.fanpiece.com/m/soccerfunnymoment/c1341289.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fsoccerfunnymoment%2Fc1341289.html&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=08df0ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://football.fanpiece.com/m/soccerfunnymoment/c1341289.html</a>"},{"pid":"7c0ebf45e8006d88a184347b2e741dc7b36d088b","tid":1023982,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"以為舊聞重溫"},{"pid":"6e19b0b3d705b12a74251560225409cf647f51e6","tid":1023982,"uid":2949,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"麥巴比已經好新<br />\n仲新麥巴比"},{"pid":"efca5b437de6e191c613f395a3abe24748cdc022","tid":1023982,"uid":92376,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"有人問個老豆係咪跟風改個仔名做麥巴比<br />\n個老豆串返果個人話我個仔出世果時麥包皮未成名囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bafebd115042636f195d6b973282fd47f279af","tid":1023982,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"忍者龜戰隊？"},{"pid":"36b105cb504871c28b649aafcee70